		<description><![CDATA[<p>Playing "out" is something that I obsessed about for around three years. I loved the sound of it but just couldn't figure out how players were doing it when they were soloing. Guys such as Allan Holdsworth, Skuli Sverrisson, Gary...</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/improvisation/how-to-play-out-when-soloing-on-bass.html">How to play &#8220;Out&#8221; when Soloing on Bass (L#100)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com">Online Bass Lessons</a>.</p>
